SELECT distinct gavius.gaviususer_id
FROM gavius LEFT JOIN cens ON gavius.gaviususer_id = cens.gaviususer_id 
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(daterequested) 
  AND (ge_name IN (${sexe}))
  AND (gu_da_0_n_name IN (${barri}))
  AND (agerange IN (${edat}))

SELECT
  "sa_name",
  (select count(*) from gavius where status = 'Approved' and llenos."sa_name" = gavius."sa_name" and $__timeFilter(daterequested)) as favorables,
  (select count(*) from gavius where status = 'Evaluating' and llenos."sa_name" = gavius."sa_name" and $__timeFilter(daterequested)) as en_curs,
  (select count(*) from gavius where status = 'Denied' and llenos."sa_name" = gavius."sa_name" and $__timeFilter(daterequested)) as desfavorables
FROM gavius as llenos
GROUP BY "sa_socialaid_id", "sa_name"
ORDER BY "sa_socialaid_id"
